item.title: Secrets of Special Forces | JoJo Siwa Now
item.description: Podcast Description JoJo is joined by her mom to give us all the behind the scenes from Special Forces, including why this show caused a rift between them. Nick Viall and Tyler Cameron were at odds from the beginning, plus insight into who JoJo thought would leave first, and a secret get together before filming even began. item.title: Harry Jowsey and Rylee Arnold | JoJo Siwa Now
item.description: Podcast Description Dancing with the Stars partners Harry Jowsey and Rylee Arnold join JoJo and reveal if they really kissed during their last dance on the show, their first impression of each other, and who they think will win the Mirrorball trophy. Plus, will Harry join Rylee on the DWTS tour?! See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information. Transcript

item.title: Jenna Johnson (Part 2) | JoJo Siwa Now
item.description: Podcast Description Part two of Jenna's episode with JoJo and she's spilling even more secrets! How did Jenna REALLY feel when she was asked to be in the first-ever same-sex couple on DWTS? Plus, find out what caused their first fight, how Jenna helped JoJo gain self-confidence, and what made them both cry! See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information. Transcript

item.title: Kalani Hilliker | JoJo Siwa Now
item.description: Podcast Description JoJo chats with her Dance Moms co-star and longtime best friend Kalani Hilliker! Kalani and JoJo reveal behind the scenes secrets from the Dance Moms Reunion … Find out which castmates didn’t show up, JoJo’s thoughts on “shading” Chloe, and how the reunion turned into one big therapy session! Plus -- JoJo FINALLY spills if she has a crush on Kalani! See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information. Transcript

item.description: Podcast Description Welcome to JoJo Siwa … Now. Get to know JoJo Siwa like never before. Dance Moms drama, falling out with friends, going through a rough breakup while on Dancing with the Stars, and how Special Forces changed her life. JoJo reveals what a day in her life is really like, the real reason the bow is gone … And why you might hear her ex on the podcast!
